data.description: Welcome to your new home at the Element, where luxury and convenience are at your fingertips. This stylish 1 bedroom,1 bathroom condo is a true gem nestled in the vibrant Atlantic Station neighborhood. The kitchen offers an open layout perfect to cook and entertain. Across from the kitchen you will find a flex space, perfect for a dining room or an office space right in your home. Tons of natural light fills the home with and with patio access from the living room and the master bedroom, this space has it all. Upgraded bathroom boasts double vanity, separate tub and glass shower, with a great size walk in closet equipped with a washer dryer for ease!      Nearby gate allows for easy street access to all the restaurants, shopping and amenities Atlantic Station has to offer. Convenient to Midtown, West Midtown, Georgia Tech, etc. Amenities include gym, pool, dog park and more. Ask listing agent about available closing cost credit by using preferred lender George Wise with Cross Country Mortgage.
